      "text": "次の現場までは10分くらいだな\n悪いな、寒いのに歩かせて",
      "startTime": 4.4833334208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい平気ですよ",
      "startTime": 7.4629252593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.573446838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "今年の仕事も……あとほんの少しですね",
      "startTime": 9.573446838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、最後まで気を引き締めていこう",
      "startTime": 14.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、任せて下さい",
      "startTime": 18.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4033.3333334000017,
          "startTime": 22.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 21.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 21.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、ここは……",
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 26
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリの会場ですね\n懐かしいです",
      "startTime": 29.72,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ここへ来ると、いろんなことを思い出します\n私達が出場した時のことももちろんですけど……",
      "startTime": 36.9766666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 41.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あの事故の日も……今日みたいに寒かったです\nとても……",
      "startTime": 46.2533333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 48
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あの日……か。そうだな、凄く寒かった\n忘れられる訳がないよな……",
      "startTime": 55.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　電話だ。もしもし……え、本当ですか！？\n分かりました、はい、はい……それでは失礼します",
      "startTime": 66.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 58.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.3333333999944,
          "startTime": 61.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14633.333333399996,
          "startTime": 73.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 74.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん？　どうしたんですか？",
      "startTime": 74.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 77.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの年明け最初のライブオファーを急遽もらった\n地上波の正月特番で大々的に生放送をするらしい",
      "startTime": 81.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大事なスタートダッシュになると思う\nその分プレッシャーは大きいけど……どうだ？",
      "startTime": 88.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……やります。やらせて下さい",
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。みんなにも確認しておくよ",
      "startTime": 95.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 99.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……5！",
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……っ",
      "startTime": 108.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、随分と遅くまで練習してるんだな\nあまり無理はするなよ？",
      "startTime": 118.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……これくらい、大丈夫、です……っ",
      "startTime": 120.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルがクリスマスイベントを成功させましたよね",
      "startTime": 128.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "月ストだって、負けられませんから",
      "startTime": 133.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "みんなのやる気も凄いんですよ\nオファーだってみんな即答だったんですよね？",
      "startTime": 140.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "それに、最近は自主練をさらに増やして\n体力だって相当ついたんです",
      "startTime": 148.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "これくらい、なんと……も……っ？",
      "startTime": 150.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃っ！　大丈夫か！？",
      "startTime": 156.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 156.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage04",
      "startTime": 159.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、ご心配をお掛けして……",
      "startTime": 160.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "軽い立ち眩みで済んで良かったよ\nでも……ちょっと琴乃らしくないな",
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私らしくない……ですか？",
      "startTime": 171.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が体調管理に気を遣ってることは知ってる\nそれなのに倒れそうになるなんて……よっぽどだぞ？",
      "startTime": 179.5866666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、月ストのみんなも帰る時に\n「無理しないでね」って言ってました……",
      "startTime": 188.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "心配させて、しかも実際に倒れちゃうなんて\nリーダー失格ですね……",
      "startTime": 196.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "活動を続けていればそういうこともある\n反省はして、後はしっかり前を向こう",
      "startTime": 201.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
